---
import Container from "./Container.astro";
---
<Container>

  <div id="aboutme" class="flex flex-row w-[1000px] h-screen mx-auto " >
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center ">
        <h2 id="heading" class="flex items-end justify-center text-slate-50 mb-4 text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">About Me</h2>
        <p class=" text-slate-300 text-2xl  lg:w-full md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl">Hi, I am <strong class="text-cyan-500">Chandrashekhar Kachawa</strong>, a React Developer from India, I am a self taught developer, FOSS lover, Linux enthusiast. I love creating something out of nothing, my dream is to create something that millions of people use. When i was little, i was always curious about how computers work. Sensei Victor Omar shown me the right path. 
        </p>
        <h5 class="text-slate-50 my-4 text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl">Here are a few technologies I've been playing with recently:</h5>
        <ul class="text-slate-300 grid grid-cols-2 gap-10 text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl">
            <li>JavaScript (ES6+)</li>
            <li>HTML & (S)CSS</li>
            <li>React js</li>
            <li>Astro</li>
            <li>Tailwind CSS</li>
            <li>Chakra UI</li>
          </ul>
    </div>
      <!-- Image -->
  <div  >
    <div id="image" class="md:h-80 md:w-80 ">
      <img id="avatar" src="/avatar.webp"  />
      <div id="filter"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</Container>

<style>
  #heading::after {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    height: 1px;
    width: 90px;
    
    background-color: rgb(45, 57, 82);
    position: relative;
    bottom: -5px;
    margin-left: 20px;
    }
    #heading::before {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    height: 1px;
    width: 90px;
    background-color: rgb(45, 57, 82);
    position: relative;
    bottom: -5px;
    margin-right: 20px;
  }
</style>